01:13:32.156 --> 01:13:34.660
Yeah, I had a talk with Ann last night.

01:13:35.452 --> 01:13:36.954
Yeah, she is pretty upset.

01:13:38.121 --> 01:13:39.331
Yeah, I know.

01:13:41.417 --> 01:13:42.377
I'm going to leave.

01:13:43.086 --> 01:13:45.088
