01:18:38.645 --> 01:18:39.646
The earth was?

01:18:39.979 --> 01:18:41.982
Yeah, the earth was really gas.

01:18:42.358 --> 01:18:45.736
And the sun formed, and it was so hot...

01:18:46.028 --> 01:18:50.534
