01:29:29.749 --> 01:29:32.670
Wake up! She is leaving the bank.

01:29:33.629 --> 01:29:35.214
Dad! Wake up!

01:29:36.715 --> 01:29:39.344
Wh... Where is... duh...

01:29:40.095 --> 01:29:41.721
I'm on my way.

01:29:42.555 --> 01:29:43.765
Oh, no.

