What do you think?

01:32:37.430 --> 01:32:38.931
Yeah, could be.

01:33:50.891 --> 01:33:52.643
Looks like a girls car to me.

01:33:53.310 --> 01:33:54.855
Could it be hers?

01:33:57.149 --> 01:33:59.735
